{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The status of the alerts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertMessage"},{"text":" background color and its icon color are based on this status.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert"},{"text":" icon and text color are based on this status.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents15OUDSAlertStatusO","symbolKind":"enum","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration","title":"OUDSAlertStatus","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@frozen","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSAlertStatus"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are two types of statuses:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Non-functional statuses used for informational or decorative alert messages."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"They provide context or highlight content without implying a specific state, system event, or user action."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"These alerts are not tied to UX patterns such as success, error, or warning, and may use contextual or brand-related icons to enhance recognition or storytelling.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Functional statuses communicate specific system statuses, results, or user feedback:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Each variant conveys a clear semantic meaning and must always be paired with its dedicated functional icon to ensure clarity and accessibility."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use functional alerts to inform user about state changes, confirmations, or issues that are directly connected to system logic or user actions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"These messages carry functional meaning and help guide user response or acknowledgment.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/accent(icon:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/info","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/negative","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/neutral(icon:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/positive","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/warning"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Enumeration-Cases","title":"Enumeration Cases"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/warning":{"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.warning","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/warning","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Used to draw attention to potential issues or upcoming changes that might affect the user’s service or experience. Warnings encourage awareness but"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"typically do not block actions."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/warning","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"warning"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/neutral(icon:)":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/neutral(icon:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/neutral(icon:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral status can be used as a generic informative alert without semantic meaning or colour association."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Suitable for a wide range of contexts — such as tips, general information, or descriptive labels — where","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"no specific feedback or urgency is required. Appropriate for help sections, dashboards, or onboarding flows.","type":"text"}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.neutral(icon:)","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"neutral"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"icon"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14OUDSComponents8OUDSIconV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OUDSIcon"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/info":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/info","type":"topic","title":"OUDSAlertStatus.info","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"info","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/info","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Info status is used to share neutral system information or service updates that do not require immediate action. Ideal for background processes or status"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"messages where users simply need to stay informed.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon."}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/positive":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/positive","type":"topic","title":"OUDSAlertStatus.positive","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"positive"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/positive","abstract":[{"text":"Positive status indicates that a task or process has been completed successfully. These alerts reassure users and confirm that no further action is needed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSInlineAlert":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSInlineAlert"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSInlineAlert"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsinlinealert","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSInlineAlert","abstract":[{"text":"Inline alert is a lightweight UI element, placed in the content flow, that displays information, system feedback,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status changes throughout short, prominent, persistent and non actionable communication. Inline alert includes functional","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"icon and semantic colour, and does not include a close button and\/or action link. Inline alert does not disappear and remains visible.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertMessage":{"abstract":[{"text":"Alert message is a UI element that displays system feedback, status changes or required action; throughout detailed, prominent, persistent and actionable","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"communication. Alert message includes functional icon and semantic colour, and may include as well a close button and\/or action link.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Alert Message does not disappear automatically and remains visible until dismissed or resolved by the user.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertmessage","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertMessage","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSAlertMessage"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSAlertMessage"}],"title":"OUDSAlertMessage"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"Components","abstract":[{"text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"text":" extensions and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/negative":{"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSAlertStatus.negative","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/negative","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"negative","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative status communicates a critical issue or error that prevents the user from proceeding until it is resolved. These alerts remain visible until"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the problem is fixed or dismissed by the user."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/negative","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/accent(icon:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSAlertStatus.accent(icon:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/accent(icon:)","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"accent","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"icon","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14OUDSComponents8OUDSIconV","text":"OUDSIcon","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent status uses brand colours to draw attention to promotional or highlighted information while remaining non-critical. Ideal for marketing content,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"announcements, or feature highlights, where you want to subtly engage users without introducing functional semantics. Ideal for promotional banners,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"product updates, or customer engagement moments."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/accent(icon:)","kind":"symbol"},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus":{"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The status of the alerts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertMessage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" background color and its icon color are based on this status."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" icon and text color are based on this status."}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}